Additional materials in the collection include University of Iowa forms and policies;
            correspondence between Oakes and members of the Jones family and Univ. of Iowa faculty;
            a set of typed transcripts of six or seven interviews conducted by Oakes with Jones
            family members, ministers, and other individuals; a set of black-and-white photographs
            of Jones, his immediate family, and Church officials; and five microfilm reels.
